"english":"the third holiest site or pilgrimage destination (Jerusalem's Temple Mount)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَرِيم (ḥarīm)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَرَام (ḥarām)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of حَرَام (ḥarām)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَرُمَ (ḥaruma) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حُرْمَة (ḥurma)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew חֵרֶם (ḥērem, “taboo, consecration”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7753","headword_ar":"حَرُمَ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuromN","text_ar":"حُرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurumN","text_ar":"حُرُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuromapN","text_ar":"حُرْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKoot, S, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromapN","text_ar":"حِرْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKoot, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, forbidden, prohibited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unlawful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harumati AlS~alaApu","text_ar":"حَرُمَتِ الصَّلَاةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuromN","text_ar":"حُرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","tex