a command or an ordinance, &c.,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a person,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, sacred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inviolable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entitled to reverence, respect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence several applications of its part. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariymN","text_ar":"حَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haramahu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"حَرَمَهُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harimahu Al$y^","text_ar":"حَرِمَهُ الشي"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarimN","text_ar":"حَرِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromN","text_ar":"حِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarimapN","text_ar":"حَرِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromapN","text_ar":"حِرْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromaAnN","text_ar":"حِرْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariymapN","text_ar":"حَرِيمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariymN","text_ar":"حَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoramapN","text_ar":"مَحْرَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Har p. 69;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrmhu","text_ar":"احرمهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$y^","text_ar":"الشي"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) but this last is of weak authority; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He denied him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refused him, the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he refused to give him the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":554},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he rendered him hopeless of the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS:) accord. to the T,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromN","text_ar":"حِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"denying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refusing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromapN","text_ar":"حِرْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromaAnN","text_ar":"حِرْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) which signifies [also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"denying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refusing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendering unprosperous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unfortunate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL;) [and frequently, as inf. n. of the pass. v."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hurima","text_ar":"حُرِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being denied prosperity; privation of prosperity; ill-fatedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurofN","text_ar":"حُرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harimato","text_ar":"حَرِمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraAmN","text_ar":"حِرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstHrmt","text_ar":"استحرمت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) said of a female cloven-hoofed animal,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She desired the male:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) accord. to El-Umawee, (S,) likewise said of a she-wolf and of a bitch: (S, K:) and sometimes also said of a she-camel: but mostly of a ewe or she-goat. (TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harima","text_ar":"حَرِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaramN","text_ar":"حَرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) accord. to AZ and Ks, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was overcome in contending for stakes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wagers, in a game of hazard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not having himself overcome therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A5-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harima","text_ar":"حَرِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaramN","text_ar":"حَرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He persisted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persisted obstinately;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persisted in contention, litigation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrangling;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he contended, litigated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrangled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","IKoot","T","TA","PS"]},{"entry_id":"n7759","headword_ar":"حَرْمٌ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromN","text_ar":"حِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7760","headword_ar":"حُرْمٌ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iHoraAm","text_ar":"اـِحْرَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on account of the performance of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haj~","text_ar":"حَجّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eumorap","text_ar":"عُمْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Az, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromN","text_ar":"حِرْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl","text_ar":"حل"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See 4 in the present art.]) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalahu fiY Hul~ihi","text_ar":"فَعَلَهُ فِى حُلِّهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waHuromihi","text_ar":"وَحُرْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Hil~ihi wa Hiromihi","text_ar":"فِى حِلِّهِ وَ حِرْمِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it when he was free from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and when he was in the state of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl","text_ar":"حل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And hence the saying of 'Áïsheh, respecting Mohammad,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotu A^uTay~ibuhu","text_ar":"كُنْتُ اُطَيِّبُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liHul~ihi waHuromihi","text_ar":"لِحُلِّهِ وَحُرْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I used to perfume him when he was free from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he was in the state of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb: *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he became free from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and when he"},{"kind":"text","text":"performed the ablution and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired to enter upon the state of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHrAm","text_ar":"احرام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haj~","text_ar":"حَجّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eumorap","text_ar":"عُمْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Az, TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huromuka","text_ar":"حُرْمُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in copies of the K, explained as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nisaAw^uka","text_ar":"نِسَاوُكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa maA taHomiY","text_ar":"وَ مَا تَحْمِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huramuka","text_ar":"حُرَمُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuromapN","text_ar":"حُرْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Az","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n7761","headword_ar":"حِرْمٌ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuromN","text_ar":"حُرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa HiromN EalaY qaroyapK A^aholakonaAhaA A^an~ahumo","text_ar":"وَ حِرْمٌ عَلَى قَرْيَةٍ اَهْلَكْنَاهَا اَنَّهُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yarojiEuwna","text_ar":"لَا يَرْجِعُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * K, * TA,) in the Kur [xxi. 95], (TA,) thus read by some, (S, TA,) means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAjibN","text_ar":"وَاجِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is a necessary lot of"},{"kind":"text","text":"the people of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a town that we have destroyed that they shall not return"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, K, TA) to their present state of existence: (TA:) so explained by Ks, (S, TA,) and by I'Ab and Fr and Zj: (TA:) some read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaromN","text_ar":"حَرْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Bd:) the people of El-Medeeneh read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forbidden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and accord. to this reading and meaning,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA","text_ar":"لا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is redundant: (TA:) [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this instance is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAjibN","text_ar":"وَاجِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromN","text_ar":"حِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for it is said that] the explanation of Ks is confirmed by the saying of 'Abd-er-Rahmán Ibn-Jumáneh [in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HmAnp","text_ar":"حمانة"},{"kind":"text","text":", app. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAnap","text_ar":"جُمَانَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",] ElMuháribee, a Jáhilee,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laA A^araY Ald~ahora baAkiyFA ↓ \n      faA_in~a HaraAmFA\n                      \n                     \n                        EalaY $ajowihi A_il~aA bakiytu EalaY EamorKw"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"For it is a necessary thing that I should not ever see one weeping for his sorrow but I should weep for 'Amr"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K","Bd"]},{"entry_id":"n7762","headword_ar":"حَرَمٌ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with which it is sometimes syn., like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamanN","text_ar":"زَمَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamaAnN","text_ar":"زَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaramu","text_ar":"الحَرَمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haram","text_ar":"حَرَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sacred territory"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Mekkeh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Az, Msb, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the limits of which were set up ancient boundary-marks"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said to have been"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"built by Abraham;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA;) also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haramu A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"حَرَمُ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haramu rasuwili A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"حَرَمُ رَسُوِلِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuHar~amu","text_ar":"المُحَرَّمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lth, K:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haram","text_ar":"حَرَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of El-Medeeneh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Medeeneh"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself:] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaramaAni","text_ar":"الحَرَمَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sacred territory"},{"kind":"page_break","n":555},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Mekkeh and that of El-Medeeneh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and El-Medeeneh"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoraAmN","text_ar":"اَحْرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haramu A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"حَرَمُ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]. (S.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariymN","text_ar":"حَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["K","Lth","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n7763","headword_ar":"حَرِمٌ","root":"Hrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAmN","text_ar":"حَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with which it is syn. (TA.) Zuheyr says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wa A_ino xaliylN yawoma masoA^alapK\n                      \n                     \n                        yaquwlu laA gaAy^ibN maAliY wa laA Harimu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And if a friend come to him, on a day of solicitation, he says, My cattle are not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my property is not, absent, nor forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refused"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, IB, TA:) [in the S, this is cited as an ex. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarimN","text_ar":"حَرِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiromaAnN","text_ar":"حِرْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haramahu","text_ar":"حَرَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.: but] IB says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harim","text_ar":"حَرِم"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mamonuwE","text_ar":"مَمْنُوع"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yqwl","text_ar":"يقول"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this verse is marfooa though commencing an apodosis, because meant to be understood as put before [in the protasis], accord. to Sb; as though the poet said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaquwlu A_ino A^ataAhu xaliylN","text_ar":"يَقُولُ اـِنْ اَتَاهُ خَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to the Koofees, it is so by reason of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa","text_ar":"فَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"understood. (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","IB","TA"]}]}}